Package: deskcleaner
Title: A Toolkit for Data Cleaning Tasks
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: "Jesse Simmons"
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a set of simple, pipeable functions to handle common 
    data cleaning and inspection tasks. The goal is to speed up the initial
    data exploration phase by automating repetitive chores like removing 
    empty rows or columns, summarizing missing values, and identifying 
    constant columns.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.1.2)
License: CC0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: false
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    tibble
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
